1
00:01:03,640 --> 00:01:05,860
[Elegy of ZhaoLi]

2
00:01:06,150 --> 00:01:09,840
[Episode 13]

3
00:01:11,450 --> 00:01:12,350
Let me in!

4
00:01:12,350 --> 00:01:14,120
- Let go!
- This is not your house.

5
00:01:14,120 --> 00:01:15,350
You can't barge in!

6
00:01:15,350 --> 00:01:16,950
As long as she's still a Jiang,

7
00:01:16,950 --> 00:01:18,480
she has to listen to me.

8
00:01:18,710 --> 00:01:19,510
Move aside!

9
00:01:19,590 --> 00:01:20,310
Enough!

10
00:01:20,430 --> 00:01:21,280
Let go!

11
00:01:22,039 --> 00:01:22,789
Stand down.

12
00:01:27,870 --> 00:01:30,590
Grand Tutor Jiang, what brings you here?

13
00:01:31,039 --> 00:01:31,590
You...

14
00:01:36,509 --> 00:01:38,460
I'm here to see my own daughter,

15
00:01:38,560 --> 00:01:40,310
in my own family's grounds.

16
00:01:40,430 --> 00:01:41,710
Do I need a reason?

17
00:01:42,759 --> 00:01:45,160
I've cut all ties
with the Jiang household.

18
00:01:45,870 --> 00:01:48,000
This garden belonged to my mother.

19
00:01:48,710 --> 00:01:51,560
The deed is now in my name.

20
00:01:52,120 --> 00:01:54,950
It has nothing to do
with you, Grand Tutor.

21
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:56,310
Li.

22
00:01:56,870 --> 00:01:59,470
Whatever happened before,
I admit I was wrong.

23
00:01:59,920 --> 00:02:02,150
But you're still my daughter.

24
00:02:02,310 --> 00:02:04,400
My blood runs in your veins.

25
00:02:04,680 --> 00:02:07,210
Bone may break,
but blood will always bind us.

26
00:02:07,280 --> 00:02:08,280
Can we talk

27
00:02:08,750 --> 00:02:11,080
somewhere private

28
00:02:11,630 --> 00:02:13,030
and clear the air?

29
00:02:17,680 --> 00:02:18,400
My Lady.

30
00:02:20,310 --> 00:02:21,030
It's fine.

31
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:23,910
Please.

32
00:02:39,910 --> 00:02:41,240
Say what you came to say.

33
00:02:42,630 --> 00:02:44,680
Your engagement to General Xun...

34
00:02:45,190 --> 00:02:46,590
Is it really called off?

35
00:02:49,430 --> 00:02:53,360
He committed unforgivable crimes
and now sits in the imperial prison.

36
00:02:53,430 --> 00:02:55,090
So of course, it's called off.

37
00:02:56,310 --> 00:03:00,110
Just stop dreaming about climbing
the ladder through powerful men.

38
00:03:00,470 --> 00:03:01,430
Then...

39
00:03:01,840 --> 00:03:04,120
what does the Empress Dowager say?

40
00:03:05,150 --> 00:03:07,080
What exactly are you trying to say?

41
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:08,910
I heard

42
00:03:09,430 --> 00:03:12,630
you've been spending a lot of time
with His Majesty lately.

43
00:03:12,630 --> 00:03:15,230
Are you planning to become
one of his consorts?

44
00:03:15,680 --> 00:03:18,280
I thought you had something
meaningful to say.

45
00:03:18,870 --> 00:03:19,750
Turns out

46
00:03:21,150 --> 00:03:23,350
you're just trying to sell me off again.

47
00:03:23,870 --> 00:03:24,840
Li,

48
00:03:25,430 --> 00:03:27,240
I'm doing this for your own good.

49
00:03:27,870 --> 00:03:29,800
I have no choice.

50
00:03:30,190 --> 00:03:31,800
I was born poor.

51
00:03:32,470 --> 00:03:33,930
No status, no foundation.

52
00:03:34,150 --> 00:03:36,710
Marriage alliances are the only way up.

53
00:03:36,710 --> 00:03:38,190
If you could become a palace consort,

54
00:03:38,190 --> 00:03:40,079
that would be a supreme honor.

55
00:03:44,360 --> 00:03:45,520
Forget it.

56
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:47,920
If you don't like hearing it,
we'll drop it.

57
00:03:48,220 --> 00:03:49,710
Look at this garden.

58
00:03:51,840 --> 00:03:54,440
It's exactly the same
as when your mother left.

59
00:03:55,120 --> 00:03:56,750
Nothing has changed.

60
00:03:58,120 --> 00:04:00,470
Did she leave you anything?

61
00:04:02,310 --> 00:04:04,120
Other than this garden,

62
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:07,280
didn't she give you everything?

63
00:04:07,750 --> 00:04:10,080
You couldn't afford the imperial exams.

64
00:04:10,120 --> 00:04:12,800
She begged and borrowed
to hire tutors for you.

65
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:14,560
That's how you got where you are today!

66
00:04:14,560 --> 00:04:15,910
And you?

67
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:19,240
How did you repay her?

68
00:04:21,540 --> 00:04:24,460
[Clouded hair, floral grace, golden pins;
she is half-drunk on splendor. Xingzhi]

69
00:04:48,480 --> 00:04:49,680
When I succeed,

70
00:04:50,870 --> 00:04:52,560
I will never fail you.

71
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:56,120
I believe in you.

72
00:05:01,310 --> 00:05:01,950
Qing.

73
00:05:02,480 --> 00:05:03,920
I'm only in eighth rank,

74
00:05:04,190 --> 00:05:06,070
yet I can already meet the Emperor.

75
00:05:06,070 --> 00:05:07,870
Heaven truly didn't let me down.

76
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:22,060
- Greetings...
- Xingzhi.

77
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:23,390
Qing.

78
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:26,070
Look, the flower you gave me

79
00:05:26,160 --> 00:05:27,120
is wilting.

80
00:05:27,830 --> 00:05:30,160
Too much water again?

81
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:31,360
You soaked the roots.

82
00:05:33,190 --> 00:05:34,770
Oh, I'm just so...

83
00:05:34,770 --> 00:05:37,700
[The late Emperor of the Zhao State]

84
00:05:39,310 --> 00:05:40,770
Greetings, Your Majesty.

85
00:05:42,510 --> 00:05:43,240
Oh, right.

86
00:05:45,480 --> 00:05:47,600
Xingzhi, this is my husband,

87
00:05:47,600 --> 00:05:49,600
Jiang Chengzhou, newly ranked scholar.

88
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:50,800
At your service.

89
00:05:58,870 --> 00:06:00,680
Qing is dear to me.

90
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:02,800
If you ever mistreat her,

91
00:06:03,070 --> 00:06:04,720
I'll hold you accountable.

92
00:06:04,830 --> 00:06:05,240
I...

93
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:07,040
I wouldn't dare.

94
00:06:07,160 --> 00:06:08,480
Never.

95
00:06:09,680 --> 00:06:12,080
Stop using your imperial airs
to scare him.

96
00:06:13,430 --> 00:06:15,090
Look at you, you're sweating.

97
00:06:15,430 --> 00:06:17,360
I'm fine. Not hot at all.

98
00:06:25,390 --> 00:06:27,120
You were just a child back then.

99
00:06:27,390 --> 00:06:29,830
- What could you know?
- Then tell me now.

100
00:06:29,830 --> 00:06:32,950
How did my mother die?

101
00:06:34,240 --> 00:06:36,430
Twelve years ago,
chaos broke out in the palace.

102
00:06:36,430 --> 00:06:38,920
But she had already saved Xie Jiuzhao.

103
00:06:38,920 --> 00:06:39,630
After that,

104
00:06:40,120 --> 00:06:42,390
we lived here.

105
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:43,950
Until one day

106
00:06:45,510 --> 00:06:47,680
she took him away

107
00:06:47,680 --> 00:06:49,310
and never returned.

108
00:06:49,680 --> 00:06:51,000
That's when you told me

109
00:06:52,560 --> 00:06:54,240
she was dead.

110
00:06:55,950 --> 00:06:56,190
Tell me.

111
00:06:56,190 --> 00:06:57,390
[Clouded hair, floral grace, golden pins,
she is half-drunk on splendor. Xingzhi]

112
00:06:58,120 --> 00:07:00,800
How did she die?

113
00:07:00,870 --> 00:07:04,500
[Clouded hair, floral grace, golden pins,
she is half-drunk on splendor. Xingzhi]

114
00:07:09,800 --> 00:07:10,730
What's so funny?

115
00:07:11,430 --> 00:07:13,310
You're just like your mother,

116
00:07:13,870 --> 00:07:15,680
loose and shameless!

117
00:07:15,950 --> 00:07:17,310
You already had one man

118
00:07:17,430 --> 00:07:20,510
- and still wanted another, didn't you?
- Don't you dare insult my mother!

119
00:07:20,510 --> 00:07:21,830
Am I wrong?

120
00:07:22,270 --> 00:07:24,480
You were engaged to Xun Simo,

121
00:07:24,830 --> 00:07:26,870
yet entangled with His Majesty!

122
00:07:27,800 --> 00:07:29,270
You and your mother

123
00:07:29,870 --> 00:07:31,240
should go to hell!

124
00:07:32,870 --> 00:07:35,360
I'll ask you one last time.

125
00:07:37,390 --> 00:07:38,680
How did

126
00:07:40,040 --> 00:07:42,310
my mother die?

127
00:07:42,950 --> 00:07:46,270
She humiliated me back then.

128
00:07:47,070 --> 00:07:48,720
So I killed her with my own hands!

129
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:49,270
You...

130
00:07:55,360 --> 00:07:58,360
Now that you've become the Grand Tutor,

131
00:07:58,680 --> 00:08:00,800
how will you repay me?

132
00:08:01,480 --> 00:08:04,360
I'll devote my life to Your Majesty

133
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:06,540
and serve you with absolute loyalty.

134
00:08:23,390 --> 00:08:24,600
Your Majesty,

135
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:27,480
why did you summon me?

136
00:08:31,750 --> 00:08:33,390
I told you it's pointless.

137
00:08:34,030 --> 00:08:36,840
Why did you insist on
sticking your nose in?

138
00:08:43,630 --> 00:08:44,750
However,

139
00:08:45,240 --> 00:08:47,030
it wasn't me who wanted you.

140
00:08:47,390 --> 00:08:48,600
Someone else

141
00:08:49,240 --> 00:08:50,750
did.

142
00:08:57,960 --> 00:08:59,120
Chengzhou?

143
00:09:22,910 --> 00:09:23,870
Chengzhou...

144
00:09:24,120 --> 00:09:27,870
Can you spare Li?

145
00:09:29,240 --> 00:09:31,120
Please...

146
00:09:38,630 --> 00:09:40,080
Jiang Chengzhou.

147
00:09:41,790 --> 00:09:44,440
You're not a father.

148
00:09:46,360 --> 00:09:48,600
You're not even human!

149
00:09:49,120 --> 00:09:51,390
I can disown you as my daughter,

150
00:09:51,510 --> 00:09:54,000
but as long as you’re a Jiang,

151
00:09:54,320 --> 00:09:55,920
you'll do this one last thing

152
00:09:56,270 --> 00:09:58,080
for your family.

153
00:09:58,720 --> 00:10:01,080
Go to the palace and beg His Majesty

154
00:10:01,510 --> 00:10:03,910
to make you his woman.

155
00:10:05,080 --> 00:10:05,790
Go!

156
00:10:07,670 --> 00:10:08,670
Now!
